46#ifndef AES_ICM_H
47#define AES_ICM_H
48
49#include "cipher.h"
50#include "datatypes.h"
51
52#ifdef OPENSSL
53
54#include <openssl/evp.h>
55#include <openssl/aes.h>
56
57typedef struct {
58 v128_t counter; /* holds the counter value */
59 v128_t offset; /* initial offset value */
60 int key_size;
61 EVP_CIPHER_CTX *ctx;
62} srtp_aes_icm_ctx_t;
63
64#endif /* OPENSSL */
65
66#ifdef NSS
67
68#include <nss.h>
69#include <pk11pub.h>
70
71typedef struct {
72 v128_t counter;
73 v128_t offset;
74 int key_size;
75 uint8_t iv[16];
76 NSSInitContext *nss;
77 PK11SymKey *key;
78 PK11Context *ctx;
79} srtp_aes_icm_ctx_t;
80
81#endif /* NSS */
82
83#endif /* AES_ICM_H */
